List ToDo

The [bold cyan]todo[/bold cyan] command list ToDo entries found in [dim]ToDo.md[/dim] files in child directories.

Files in directories containing [yellow]_archived[/yellow] in their path are automatically skipped.

[bold green]$[/bold green] [bold]todo list[/bold]         [dim]# List todo entries[/dim]
[bold green]$[/bold green] [bold]todo edit[/bold] [yellow]project[/yellow]  [dim]# Open a project's ToDo file in the editor[/dim]
